text: Hum roz jo khana khate hain, uski quality pe hum rarely dhyaan dete hain.
Street food aur takeaway humari daily life ka hissa ban chuka hai.
Par hygiene aur cleanliness ko hum aksar ignore kar dete hain.
Agar hum thoda conscious banein, better choices possible hain.
Healthy food ek habit ban sakta hai, agar hum chahein.
